{"url": "https://people.com/style/bella-hadid-poses-pantsless-in-giuseppe-zanotti-ads/", "text": "Mert Alas and Marcus Piggott\n\nAt this point, Gigi Hadid does so many fashion advertising campaigns (with new ones dropping practically every month) that it\u2019s hardly breaking news anymore. But last year, we discovered an interesting trend in her poses. It seems that somewhere in her contract it\u2019s written that \u201cpants are not required.\u201d From Stuart Weitzman to Tommy Hilfiger and even Reebok ads, Gigi has a pattern of going pantsless on set. And now it looks like she gave a few pointers to little sis Bella Hadid, because her latest Giuseppe Zanotti campaign looks straight from Gigi\u2019s posing playbook.\n\nMert Alas and Marcus Piggott\n\nBella just reprised her role with the designer shoe brand as the star of its spring 2018 campaign (she previously modeled in the fall 2017 collection ads). And while the shoot shows her throwing her signature sharp-eyed stares, we couldn\u2019t help but notice that her pantsless bodysuit look is surprisingly similar to Gigi\u2019s past campaigns.\n\nThe shoot was photographed by Mert Alas and Marcus Piggott and styled by the famed Carine Roitfeld who all have close relationships with Bella, which resulted in \u201cgreat energy\u201d on set.\n\nThe inspiration behind the photos was of an \u201cendless summer\u201d which was channeled through a \u201990s vibe (re: the high pony and high-cut leotard).\n\nMert Alas and Marcus Piggott\n\n\u201cThis campaign really represents the authentic energy of the brand\u2014modern, sensual, powerful,\u201d Zanotti said in the press release. \u201cAnd then there\u2019s Bella, back for a second season, who brings with her a rock-and-roll attitude that\u2019s also playful and seductive. The overall effect is compelling, contemporary, arresting.\u201d\n\nMert Alas and Marcus Piggott\n\nHow It\u2019s Done: Bella Hadid\u2019s Sexy Cat Eyes\n\nIn the ads she models the Kendra bootie, the Eliza light blue slingback, the Aleesha slide with serpent-shaped anklet and the Agnes green stilettos all styled sans pants which no doubt would make Gigi proud.", "images": ["https://people.com/thmb/BDPIxJbrTLGmVX3TUk08u7O56Y0=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(599x0:601x2)/vanessa-hudgens-5-76c25640fe674b999afaf34c25545310.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/7ggAdQqCIheSQ9F7tVlKCbgEhrA=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(979x599:981x601)/kendall-jenner-gigi-hadid-1-9496bfcd11084ebca222ce11f9cb61f0.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/I9ErgEEx9VgFbCT5HCncPb0A_DQ=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(646x0:648x2)/anne-hathaway-neiman-marcus-new-york-fashion-week-091622-49dd3ae5a4364c888d1a0b89b8fcc9f2.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/CYo8AVfYFR-TCnGxcmhIriFDUkE=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(749x0:751x2)/denim-icon-tout-d34e72073def4919a33344d71a0a3f6b.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/vQs4H9wIdvENEvOGTV5ORAHY1uU=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(872x264:874x266)/Venus-Williams-Reinstein-Ross-Goldsmiths-111523-tout-a51b33e8b05646de99edf20f4dab9473.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/m9KTf2ku1wjSQHJY5Q7PWhumajw=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(734x9:736x11)/lily-james-1-e3482f5123b549558b41f96a6fa142a6.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/FImbjqXZbZfbI1H9enQhOknDwSI=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(749x194:751x196)/Rachel-Parcell-083023-tout-fdb5353c34ed42998d5b92961895f8fe.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/x73ackE3QQ2vBxU5KDuE_CwVkb0=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(575x231:577x233)/kendall-jenner-met-gala-050123-d5c4a7ed01a84c688158b7ab27cc5ed4.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/Lje7sGaj3HgeS-yLg9z5JSNPfrU=/300x150/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/people_magazine_sub-e6689738996d40f38f154099e1751481.png", "https://people.com/thmb/